Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.04,0:00:39.93,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,For one still so young, \Nyour calligraphy is highly conformist.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.52,0:00:44.80,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if it's better \Ndescribed as copybook-style,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.80,0:00:47.47,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,or made simply to win calligraphy awards.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.06,0:00:52.12,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you even attempt to scale \Nthe wall of mediocrity?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.82,0:00:59.20,MX Calligraphy 5,,0000,0000,0000,,Eika Prize Award Reception
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.36,0:00:55.36,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,With all due respect, Director...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.70,0:00:58.91,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,Managing the hall for many years \Nhas given me a discerning eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.89,0:01:01.86,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,And your calligraphy is just plain dull.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.71,0:01:06.38,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, I took these photos earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.04,0:01:08.43,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Handa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.61,0:01:12.02,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with my calligraphy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.80,0:01:23.88,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, you idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.88,0:01:26.67,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go! He can't insult me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.67,0:01:29.58,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't even know how hard I've worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.58,0:01:30.29,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.04,0:01:45.91,MX Signs 6,,0000,0000,0000,,1 New Message
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.91,0:01:47.41,MX Signs 6,,0000,0000,0000,,From Kawafuji\NSub [None]\N\NHow's the island?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.22,0:01:50.42,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not much to it...
