Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.98,0:03:38.98,MX Handwritten 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Haneda Airport: SNA033 dpt 10:00\NNagasaki Airport: arrive 11:50\NNagasaki Airport: AHA 4674 dpt 13:20\NFukue Airport: arrive 14:00\N\NBoard taxi at Fukue Airport. \NAfter you arrive at location on map,\Ncontact Village Chief Kido Yuujirou. \NDo not act rude.\N\N- Seimei
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.61,0:03:42.11,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yer lucky, sonny!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.76,0:03:44.76,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I hadn't come by,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.76,0:03:47.81,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,it mighta taken you more'n half \Na day get to Nanatsutake Village!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.81,0:03:48.37,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.95,0:03:50.77,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mighta taken half a day's walk!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.77,0:03:53.82,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I can't understand what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.82,0:03:55.64,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Whaddya say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.64,0:03:56.36,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.36,0:03:57.09,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.77,0:03:59.96,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ain't got no clue what yer sayin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.96,0:04:02.38,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever. I'll just ignore him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.30,0:04:06.81,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing here...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.14,0:04:08.69,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look there, sonny!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.69,0:04:10.44,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's th'sea! Th'sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.44,0:04:11.22,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Th'sea"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.39,0:04:13.29,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.25,0:04:17.84,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What d'you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.84,0:04:20.44,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My grandkid sure loves th'sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.62,0:04:23.21,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Always a-squealin' with glee at th'sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.54,0:04:24.57,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's to think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.31,0:04:26.95,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just the ocean...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.03,0:04:32.08,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it doesn't look pretty \Nbecause my heart's gone hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.41,0:04:35.17,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, my ribs...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.17,0:04:37.64,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This's as far as I take you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.00,0:04:40.15,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta get to th'field.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.15,0:04:40.75,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.28,0:04:44.72,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The sea not lookin' pretty to you, sonny,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.72,0:04:46.72,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,ain't 'cause your heart's gone hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.65,0:04:49.65,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just 'cuz it gets cloudy in th'afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.65,0:04:52.21,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... so that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.47,0:04:56.66,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Th'sea's worth seein' 'specially \Nwhen your heart's gone hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.66,0:04:58.27,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You just don' see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.19,0:05:02.90,MX Signs 5,,0000,0000,0000,,Kijima Shipping
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.64,0:05:02.90,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Handa-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.91,0:05:04.86,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Handa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.82,0:05:10.91,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Handa-san! It's Kijima Shipping!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.91,0:05:11.54,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.21,0:05:12.87,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.29,0:05:15.98,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kijima Shipping!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.12,0:05:21.11,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That should be everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.11,0:05:24.71,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, could you help me bring them inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.73,0:05:28.43,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, our company doesn't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.81,0:05:29.79,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.00,0:05:34.71,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Customer service turns lousy when \Nthey don't have any competitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.71,0:05:36.11,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.85,0:05:39.34,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Er, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.73,0:05:41.25,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Village Chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.25,0:05:43.59,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've had a long trip from Tokyo, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.59,0:05:45.02,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your house key.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.45,0:05:49.11,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Does this place have no buses, \Nor trains, or anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.57,0:05:51.64,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A bus stops by once a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.64,0:05:55.70,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can call for a taxi, \Nbut there aren't many of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.70,0:05:58.50,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can borrow my car when \Nyou need to go to town.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.04,0:06:02.77,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, could you \Nleave me alone for a week?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.77,0:06:04.74,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to immerse myself in writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.74,0:06:06.23,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.79,0:06:09.72,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, let me try the key.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.21,0:06:11.85,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Take all the time you need for writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.43,0:06:14.68,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't have to worry about food, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.68,0:06:15.90,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, that easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.40,0:06:23.90,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.42,0:06:27.34,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nobody living here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.34,0:06:29.11,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.79,0:06:32.56,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels strangely lived-in, somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.02,0:06:34.08,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.78,0:06:35.69,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.17,0:06:38.16,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're... You're just imagining it, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.26,0:06:47.13,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Talismans?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.13,0:06:49.25,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, don't worry about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.70,0:06:51.45,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're just talismans.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.78,0:06:59.26,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A pit toilet...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.00,0:07:03.95,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.14,0:07:07.45,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Never used a balanced-flue \Nbath heater before?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.26,0:07:12.68,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You crank this to light the flame.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.10,0:07:14.12,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.64,0:07:20.50,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to live in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.44,0:07:31.59,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.20,0:07:34.43,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.20,0:07:41.76,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,There's definitely something in here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.62,0:07:49.46,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You found me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.25,0:07:53.88,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Village Chief! Who is this kid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.88,0:07:55.82,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the village scamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.82,0:07:57.82,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems she's made this house her base.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.82,0:07:58.80,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Base?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.80,0:08:01.08,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, more of a colony, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.33,0:08:03.61,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, that makes even less sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.61,0:08:04.81,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terribly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.81,0:08:06.81,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I told her to leave, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.81,0:08:08.46,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, mister! You a Junon Boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.46,0:08:09.11,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.11,0:08:11.84,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Naru! It's rude to ask questions like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.15,0:08:15.96,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But Miwa-nee was sayin', \NJunon Boys look really cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.96,0:08:19.41,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy looks really cool, \Nso he's a Junon Boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.41,0:08:23.69,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not entirely incorrect, \Nbut this man is a master calligrapher.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.23,0:08:25.99,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! I get it, Village Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.49,0:08:28.85,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a Junon Boy who can also do calligraphy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.85,0:08:30.34,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.34,0:08:32.73,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I still think he's a Junon Boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.73,0:08:35.86,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But he's past the age where \Nyou'd call him a "boy," see?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.36,0:08:35.86,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.47,0:08:39.86,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't people on TV claim \Nthey're younger'n they are?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.86,0:08:40.87,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Miwa-nee said...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.21,0:08:40.87,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.52,0:08:44.83,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, fudgin' numbers in their \Nfavor may just be part of the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:48.59,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! And "cowboys" are "boys" \Neven when they're old!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.50,0:08:53.73,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.73,0:08:55.36,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That child never listens.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.36,0:08:57.43,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, could you leave, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.29,0:09:00.10,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,He locked it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.60,0:09:02.24,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.42,0:09:06.16,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is her "base," huh? Like hell it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.64,0:09:11.29,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's lucky for me that it already \Nhas some semblance of living space.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.01,0:09:18.95,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna write, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.95,0:09:20.30,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you get in here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.17,0:09:34.63,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,Who does he think he is? \NJust because he won a prize.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.89,0:09:37.07,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,He punched the exhibit hall director.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.07,0:09:39.37,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,Now he's basically dead \Nto the calligraphy world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.37,0:09:40.68,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,He has no manners.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.19,0:09:43.91,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk to him. They might \Nthink you're like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.91,0:09:45.56,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't have anything to do with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.56,0:09:47.77,MX Calligraphy 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Spring Summer \NFall Winter\N\NPraying To \NDeaf Ears\N\NIndependence And \NSelf-Respect\N\NEnemies On \NAll Sides
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.33,0:09:50.08,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.08,0:09:51.75,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I keep getting distracted!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.13,0:09:56.58,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a kettle in this house?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.58,0:09:59.91,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta eat Corn Cones in stacks like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.91,0:10:02.87,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got metabolic syndrome, \Nso one at a time's plenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.19,0:10:03.92,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.92,0:10:05.84,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Handa-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.84,0:10:07.64,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Want some finger-corn?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.46,0:10:10.38,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Roll, roll...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.03,0:10:13.56,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! A new technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.56,0:10:15.50,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's pretty cool, Naru!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.50,0:10:17.92,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Teach me how, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.11,0:10:17.92,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do calligraphy like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.92,0:10:20.55,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Focus... focus... focus...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.26,0:10:24.31,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.31,0:10:25.56,MX Handwritten 3,,0000,0000,0000,,Kotoishi \NNaru
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.48,0:10:25.56,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! Pretty good, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.15,0:10:28.33,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I say you could write anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.33,0:10:31.43,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so uptight, Junon Boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.79,0:10:34.30,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I'm not a Junon Boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.71,0:10:37.39,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like you have the \Nname "Kotoishi Naru"...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.39,0:10:38.65,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a name, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.39,0:10:41.75,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How'd you know my name?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.75,0:10:43.87,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You a psychic?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.87,0:10:47.50,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really that stupid, \Nor do you think I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.50,0:10:50.48,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know your name too, Junon Boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.75,0:10:54.46,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.46,0:10:55.59,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.82,0:10:57.36,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.36,0:11:00.66,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Village Chief was sayin' before...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.75,0:11:02.91,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,By golly!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.91,0:11:04.43,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty outdated cry of realization...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.79,0:11:06.38,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Junon Takeo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.64,0:11:09.89,MX Calligraphy 4,,0000,0000,0000,,Handa\NSeishuu
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.60,0:11:12.20,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Handa Seishuu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.61,0:11:14.81,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Junon aside, where'd you get Takeo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.38,0:11:18.28,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This's like a middle schooler's pen name!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.28,0:11:19.61,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's "pseudonym"!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.03,0:11:28.48,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazin'! Your calligraphy's real good, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.94,0:11:30.25,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It better be.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.64,0:11:33.48,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like how my teacher at school writes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.94,0:11:36.94,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,Your calligraphy is highly conformist.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.31,0:11:39.68,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if it's better \Ndescribed as copybook-style...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.08,0:11:42.09,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,Your calligraphy is just plain dull.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.80,0:11:45.30,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right! For dinner, Village Chief—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.71,0:11:47.56,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doin'?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.56,0:11:49.35,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You worked hard to write that so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.35,0:11:50.59,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.59,0:11:52.10,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you know about my writing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.55,0:11:53.96,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk like you know anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.35,0:11:55.03,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.68,0:11:57.02,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.06,0:12:10.87,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm horrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.35,0:12:16.09,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,What's a grown man doing, flipping out \Nwhenever someone hits the bull's eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.44,0:12:18.34,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You're going to an island?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.91,0:12:20.17,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.93,0:12:23.88,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad said... I should go cool my head...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.61,0:12:28.32,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,He said, "You're still flawed as a human \Nbeing, let alone a calligrapher."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.38,0:12:30.93,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you laughing about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.93,0:12:38.90,MX Signs 7,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawafuji\NHouse of the Arts
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.59,0:12:35.87,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,You punched an old man who \Nuses a cane. You get no sympathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.89,0:12:38.90,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,You could apologize, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.10,0:12:40.50,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.34,0:12:43.40,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad and that geezer just don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.22,0:12:46.97,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with being \Nfaithful to the fundamentals?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.92,0:12:48.62,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,Look...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.29,0:12:51.03,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,Is writing calligraphy that way
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.03,0:12:52.25,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,any fun for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.11,0:12:57.99,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a given that the fundamentals \Nmake the most beautiful writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.93,0:13:00.55,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not wrong about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.91,0:13:13.71,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...the most important thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.71,0:13:15.30,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the most important thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:18.31,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,She heard me singing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.67,0:13:21.17,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well? What's the most important thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.17,0:13:22.28,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Well? Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.73,0:13:24.12,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.12,0:13:25.15,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.36,0:13:28.07,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why should you apologize?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.96,0:13:31.61,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who was pesterin' you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.24,0:13:33.40,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So anyhow,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.40,0:13:35.54,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried rewritin' your words.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.67,0:13:39.54,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I just couldn't write 'em the way you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.59,0:13:50.35,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.48,0:13:52.31,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.08,0:13:54.99,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't do anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.36,0:13:58.11,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, you forgive me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.45,0:13:59.19,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.60,0:14:01.43,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to even forgive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.73,0:14:04.81,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.85,0:14:09.91,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad you forgave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.56,0:14:12.88,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was mighty scared of apologizin' to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.88,0:14:14.87,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But now I'm really glad I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.43,0:14:16.93,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I yelled at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.93,0:14:17.66,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.49,0:14:20.86,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.48,0:14:24.12,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.12,0:14:24.80,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.39,0:14:31.86,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, you worked hard to write this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.86,0:14:34.56,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, it was easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.93,0:14:37.73,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You write just like the copybook!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.23,0:14:45.79,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you do that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.79,0:14:47.44,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, just a reflex.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.97,0:14:51.71,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, you don't even get why I was upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.74,0:14:56.88,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just practice calligraphy, \Nso it's meant to be thrown awa—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.37,0:15:05.63,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it to me first!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.36,0:15:12.03,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.80,0:15:13.55,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.69,0:15:14.51,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sen—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.32,0:15:18.81,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go scarin' me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.81,0:15:20.94,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you up an' died!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.94,0:15:23.08,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm about to die in these heavy clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.44,0:15:26.78,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the problem with you city folk!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.78,0:15:27.61,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When that happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.17,0:15:29.74,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.08,0:15:31.10,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.35,0:15:34.74,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,First, plug up the neck of your T-shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.56,0:15:37.84,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,An' catch a bunch of air under your shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.79,0:15:41.30,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you just swim!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.45,0:15:45.92,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm impressed, in spite of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.73,0:15:57.16,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you always swim in water this deep?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.16,0:15:57.89,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.11,0:16:00.44,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,The power of childhood is terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.97,0:16:04.05,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sensei! I'm gonna show \Nyou somethin' real nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.05,0:16:04.56,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.98,0:16:08.82,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you climb that there wall, \Nyou can see a mighty fine sunset!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.59,0:16:12.92,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.92,0:16:14.63,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're climbing this bulwark?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.00,0:16:17.16,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep! Gotta climb to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.89,0:16:19.67,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need to see the sunset.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.17,0:16:20.95,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.03,0:16:24.02,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't see anything \Nthrough all those clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.70,0:16:27.38,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't know 'til you climb up and see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.82,0:16:30.47,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't try, you don't get to look.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.87,0:16:32.47,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.48,0:16:36.60,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all right. Just got in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.99,0:16:42.23,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.42,0:16:45.15,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry on up, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.36,0:16:48.35,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't climb up here, \Nyou won't get to see nothin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.80,0:16:50.61,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.46,0:16:54.48,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,even attempt to scale the wall of mediocrity?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.52,0:17:15.26,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.60,0:17:16.65,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ain't it pretty?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.48,0:17:21.28,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.62,0:17:23.64,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.06,0:17:34.69,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yer back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.99,0:17:36.47,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,First Villager?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.47,0:17:38.17,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Grampa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.17,0:17:40.16,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's your grandfather?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.32,0:17:41.15,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.83,0:17:44.08,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.08,0:17:46.83,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Better hurry on down or \NI'll open yer boxes myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.05,0:17:48.73,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.73,0:17:51.80,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yer movin' in, so I done come to pitch in!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.32,0:17:53.36,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Pitch in"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.96,0:17:58.77,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yer from Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.33,0:18:02.56,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a mighty long way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.74,0:18:06.18,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be lettin' ourselves in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.18,0:18:07.60,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.11,0:18:10.69,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon! You too, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.98,0:18:13.00,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did your grandfather call them over?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.71,0:18:15.76,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? No, he didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.25,0:18:19.20,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever'body saw the moving \Nvan and came themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.57,0:18:21.42,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not many people move in 'round here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.92,0:18:24.23,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, they don't know me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.23,0:18:26.41,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't make them do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.41,0:18:28.50,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My, what a fine young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.90,0:18:31.28,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry we took so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.28,0:18:32.62,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hina!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.63,0:18:35.56,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, lemme introduce you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.56,0:18:37.26,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This's my friend, Hina!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.88,0:18:39.23,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.65,0:18:42.60,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hina's mighty shy, y'see!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.59,0:18:46.47,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I shouldn't talk to you, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.60,0:18:49.70,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.10,0:18:52.90,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like Hina wants you \Nto pay attention to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.51,0:18:55.76,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.53,0:18:59.49,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.25,0:19:02.20,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hina cries even when she's happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.20,0:19:03.32,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is hard to deal with!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.74,0:19:05.16,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Butt jab!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.07,0:19:09.12,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You were wide open!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.36,0:19:11.06,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Kenta!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.06,0:19:14.08,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you in our class meeting \Nthat butt jabs ain't allowed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.08,0:19:15.75,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, stinky smoke-man!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.90,0:19:18.34,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry 'bout that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.69,0:19:21.37,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That punk won't shape up, \Nno matter what I tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.37,0:19:22.78,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.78,0:19:23.97,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.60,0:19:26.89,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.44,0:19:29.10,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The head teacher at the branch school.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.60,0:19:30.73,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.73,0:19:34.69,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh, ain't nothin' funnier than seein' \Na handsome guy gettin' disgraced.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.45,0:19:37.32,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.70,0:19:40.74,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mind if we bring the boxes in?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.74,0:19:42.15,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.27,0:19:56.42,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, see you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.79,0:19:57.62,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.54,0:20:34.17,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey, Kawafuji...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.16,0:20:35.84,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.31,0:20:40.26,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I kind of see the reason why \NDad had me come to this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.43,0:20:43.45,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I write anything good, \NI'll send it for display.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.45,0:20:44.91,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can help out then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.46,0:20:46.20,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.72,0:20:48.53,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you apologize to the director for me?
